  <brief_title>Follow-up Study for Patients Who Completed Study ALX0681-C301 (Post-HERCULES)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Follow-up Study for Patients Who Completed Study ALX0681-C301 (HERCULES) to Evaluate Long-term Safety and Efficacy of Caplacizumab (Post-HERCULES)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
