  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate long-term safety and efficacy of caplacizumab, to
      evaluate safety and efficacy of repeated use of caplacizumab and to characterize long term
      impact of TTP.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
